`I вКЖ X` is finite and `x вИИ I`, then `x вИИ A`has small conditional variance conditioned on `y вИИ A`
for each `y вИИ I \ {x}`. -/
theorem small_condVar_of_isNIPWith (isNIPWith_рЭУЭ : IsNIPWith d (рЭУЭ : Set (Set X)))
    (hA : вИАбµР ѕЙ вИВќЉ, A ѕЙ вИИ рЭУЭ) : condVar (MeasurableSpace.generateFrom sorry) (fun ѕЙ => (A ѕЙ).indicator 1 x) ќЉ вЙ§ вК§ := by
  exact le_top
